title: Ep 12 | It's Engagement Season! Our engagement stories...and yours!
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description: It's most definitely engagement season... every time I scroll down my feed, I see another person getting engaged. So today we're gonna chat about our very own engagement stories and we're gonna share some of the ones you sent in! Watch us on youtube on Kristen Leanne's channel!
